    id: 'prompt-34',
    prompt: 'Create a comprehensive weekly stress management schedule by planning and blocking out specific times for 5 different stress-reducing activities in your calendar',
    category: 'planning',
    helpText: 'Proactive scheduling ensures stress management becomes a consistent priority rather than something you only remember during crisis moments. Choose 5 specific activities like exercise, meditation, meal prep, social time, and hobby engagement, then assign each a dedicated time slot in your weekly calendar as you would any important appointment. Block out realistic time periods (15-60 minutes) at times when you are most likely to follow through, treating these commitments as non-negotiable to build sustainable stress prevention habits.'
  }
];</parameter>
<parameter name="new_string">  {
    id: 'prompt-34',
    prompt: 'Create a comprehensive weekly stress management schedule by planning and blocking out specific times for 5 different stress-reducing activities in your calendar',
