  },
  {
    id: 'prompt-35',
    prompt: 'Create a personalized stress relief kit by gathering 5 specific items that provide instant comfort during stressful moments and organizing them in one portable container',
    category: 'action',
    helpText: 'Having a physical stress relief kit provides immediate comfort and grounding during overwhelming moments when mental techniques might feel inaccessible. Choose items that engage your senses like essential oils, stress balls, calming music playlist, comfort snacks, photos of loved ones, or small meaningful objects that bring peace. Organize these items in a small bag or box that you can access quickly at home, work, or while traveling, creating a tangible reminder that you have tools available to support yourself during difficult times.'
  }
];</parameter>
